            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>别大意！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E4%BC%9A%E6%82%A3%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E4%BC%9A%E6%82%A3%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#年轻人也会患高血压#</span></a>】一个多月前，河南洛阳一初中生经常感到头晕，测量后发现其血压值较高。医生介绍：目前，我国高血压发病人群低龄化趋势明显。除遗传因素外，长期过量饮酒吸烟、精神紧张、缺乏运动、高盐饮食等，都是导致此现象的主要原因。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#部分早期高血压患者没有任何症状#</span></a>，或者症状不明显，需提高警惕。如何管好自己的血压？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4902303640256559" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1he12wtel8uj618w0p9e4z02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/cYhTWXAzlx085vaNCj4s01041201Fntj0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cwn